// ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
// D-Chemistry — Complete Prisma Schema
// Institute of Chemistry by Debajyoti Haldar
// ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

generator client {
  provider = "prisma-client-js"
}

datasource db {
  provider = "postgresql"
  url      = env("DATABASE_URL")
}

// ── Authentication & Users ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────

enum Role {
  STUDENT
  TEACHER
  ADMIN
}

enum Board {
  ICSE
  ISC
  CBSE
  JEE
  NEET
}

enum StudentClass {
  CLASS_10
  CLASS_11
  CLASS_12
}

enum Language {
  EN
  BN
}

model User {
  id           String   @id @default(uuid())
  email        String   @unique
  phone        String?  @unique
  passwordHash String?
  role         Role     @default(STUDENT)
  googleId     String?  @unique
  fcmToken     String?
  isActive     Boolean  @default(true)
  createdAt    DateTime @default(now())
  updatedAt    DateTime @updatedAt

  // Relations
  profile                Profile?
  enrollments            Enrollment[]
  testAttempts           TestAttempt[]
  videoProgress          VideoProgress[]
  doubts                 Doubt[]
  doubtReplies           DoubtReply[]
  payments               Payment[]
  notifications          Notification[]
  notificationPreference NotificationPreference?
  announcements          Announcement[]           @relation("AnnouncementCreator")
  refreshTokens          RefreshToken[]
  chatConversations      ChatConversation[]

  @@map("users")
}

model Profile {
  id             String        @id @default(uuid())
  userId         String        @unique
  name           String
  avatar         String?
  class          StudentClass?
  board          Board?
  language       Language      @default(EN)
  bio            String?
  streak         Int           @default(0)
  lastActiveDate DateTime?

  // Relations
  user User @relation(fields: [userId], references: [id], onDelete: Cascade)

  @@map("profiles")
}

model RefreshToken {
  id        String   @id @default(uuid())
  userId    String
  token     String   @unique
  expiresAt DateTime
  createdAt DateTime @default(now())

  // Relations
  user User @relation(fields: [userId], references: [id], onDelete: Cascade)

  @@index([userId])
  @@map("refresh_tokens")
}

model OtpCode {
  id        String   @id @default(uuid())
  email     String
  code      String
  expiresAt DateTime
  used      Boolean  @default(false)
  createdAt DateTime @default(now())

  @@index([email, code])
  @@map("otp_codes")
}

// ── Course & Content ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

model Subject {
  id          String   @id @default(uuid())
  name        String
  slug        String   @unique
  description String?
  icon        String?
  order       Int      @default(0)
  createdAt   DateTime @default(now())
  updatedAt   DateTime @updatedAt

  // Relations
  chapters Chapter[]
  batches  BatchSubject[]

  @@map("subjects")
}

model Chapter {
  id          String   @id @default(uuid())
  subjectId   String
  name        String
  description String?
  order       Int      @default(0)
  createdAt   DateTime @default(now())
  updatedAt   DateTime @updatedAt

  // Relations
  subject       Subject        @relation(fields: [subjectId], references: [id], onDelete: Cascade)
  topics        Topic[]
  formulaSheets FormulaSheet[]

  @@index([subjectId])
  @@map("chapters")
}

model Topic {
  id          String   @id @default(uuid())
  chapterId   String
  name        String
  description String?
  order       Int      @default(0)
  createdAt   DateTime @default(now())
  updatedAt   DateTime @updatedAt

  // Relations
  chapter    Chapter     @relation(fields: [chapterId], references: [id], onDelete: Cascade)
  lessons    Lesson[]
  questions  Question[]
  flashCards FlashCard[]

  @@index([chapterId])
  @@map("topics")
}

enum LessonType {
  VIDEO
  PDF
  ARTICLE
  DPP
}

model Lesson {
  id           String     @id @default(uuid())
  topicId      String
  type         LessonType
  title        String
  description  String?
  videoUrl     String?
  pdfUrl       String?
  content      String?    @db.Text
  thumbnailUrl String?
  duration     Int?       // seconds
  isFree       Boolean    @default(false)
  order        Int        @default(0)
  createdAt    DateTime   @default(now())
  updatedAt    DateTime   @updatedAt

  // Relations
  topic            Topic           @relation(fields: [topicId], references: [id], onDelete: Cascade)
  videoProgress    VideoProgress[]
  doubts           Doubt[]
  liveClassRecording LiveClass?    @relation("LiveClassRecording")

  @@index([topicId])
  @@map("lessons")
}

model VideoProgress {
  id            String   @id @default(uuid())
  userId        String
  lessonId      String
  position      Float    @default(0) // seconds
  duration      Float    @default(0)
  completed     Boolean  @default(false)
  lastWatchedAt DateTime @default(now())

  // Relations
  user   User   @relation(fields: [userId], references: [id], onDelete: Cascade)
  lesson Lesson @relation(fields: [lessonId], references: [id], onDelete: Cascade)

  @@unique([userId, lessonId])
  @@map("video_progress")
}

// ── Test & MCQ Engine ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

enum Difficulty {
  EASY
  MEDIUM
  HARD
}

enum QuestionType {
  MCQ
  INTEGER
}

enum ExamType {
  JEE_MAIN
  JEE_ADVANCED
  NEET
  ISC
  ICSE
  CBSE
  WBJEE
}

model Question {
  id           String       @id @default(uuid())
  text         String       @db.Text
  options      Json         // QuestionOption[]
  correctIndex Int
  explanation  String       @db.Text
  topicId      String
  difficulty   Difficulty   @default(MEDIUM)
  type         QuestionType @default(MCQ)
  pyqYear      Int?
  examType     ExamType?
  imageUrl     String?
  createdAt    DateTime     @default(now())
  updatedAt    DateTime     @updatedAt

  // Relations
  topic         Topic          @relation(fields: [topicId], references: [id], onDelete: Cascade)
  testSections  TestSectionQuestion[]
  testResponses TestResponse[]

  @@index([topicId])
  @@index([examType, pyqYear])
  @@map("questions")
}

enum TestType {
  PRACTICE
  MOCK
  CHAPTER
  PYQ
}

model Test {
  id              String    @id @default(uuid())
  title           String
  description     String?
  type            TestType
  duration        Int       // minutes
  totalMarks      Int
  negativeMarking Float     @default(0)
  batchId         String?
  isPublished     Boolean   @default(false)
  scheduledAt     DateTime?
  createdAt       DateTime  @default(now())
  updatedAt       DateTime  @updatedAt

  // Relations
  batch    Batch?        @relation(fields: [batchId], references: [id], onDelete: SetNull)
  sections TestSection[]
  attempts TestAttempt[]

  @@index([batchId])
  @@index([type])
  @@map("tests")
}

model TestSection {
  id               String @id @default(uuid())
  testId           String
  name             String
  marksPerQuestion Int    @default(4)
  negativeMarks    Float  @default(1)
  order            Int    @default(0)

  // Relations
  test      Test                  @relation(fields: [testId], references: [id], onDelete: Cascade)
  questions TestSectionQuestion[]

  @@index([testId])
  @@map("test_sections")
}

model TestSectionQuestion {
  id            String @id @default(uuid())
  testSectionId String
  questionId    String
  order         Int    @default(0)

  // Relations
  testSection TestSection @relation(fields: [testSectionId], references: [id], onDelete: Cascade)
  question    Question    @relation(fields: [questionId], references: [id], onDelete: Cascade)

  @@unique([testSectionId, questionId])
  @@map("test_section_questions")
}

model TestAttempt {
  id               String    @id @default(uuid())
  userId           String
  testId           String
  score            Float     @default(0)
  totalMarks       Int       @default(0)
  correctCount     Int       @default(0)
  incorrectCount   Int       @default(0)
  unattemptedCount Int       @default(0)
  percentile       Float?
  rank             Int?
  startedAt        DateTime  @default(now())
  submittedAt      DateTime?
  timeTaken        Int?      // seconds

  // Relations
  user      User           @relation(fields: [userId], references: [id], onDelete: Cascade)
  test      Test           @relation(fields: [testId], references: [id], onDelete: Cascade)
  responses TestResponse[]

  @@index([userId])
  @@index([testId])
  @@map("test_attempts")
}

model TestResponse {
  id               String  @id @default(uuid())
  attemptId        String
  questionId       String
  selectedOption   Int?
  integerAnswer    Int?
  isCorrect        Boolean @default(false)
  isMarkedForReview Boolean @default(false)
  timeSpent        Int     @default(0) // seconds

  // Relations
  attempt  TestAttempt @relation(fields: [attemptId], references: [id], onDelete: Cascade)
  question Question   @relation(fields: [questionId], references: [id], onDelete: Cascade)

  @@unique([attemptId, questionId])
  @@map("test_responses")
}

// ── Batch & Enrollment ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

model Batch {
  id           String       @id @default(uuid())
  name         String
  description  String?
  class        StudentClass
  board        Board
  isFree       Boolean      @default(false)
  price        Float        @default(0)
  inviteCode   String?      @unique
  isActive     Boolean      @default(true)
  startDate    DateTime?
  endDate      DateTime?
  createdAt    DateTime     @default(now())
  updatedAt    DateTime     @updatedAt

  // Relations
  enrollments   Enrollment[]
  subjects      BatchSubject[]
  tests         Test[]
  liveClasses   LiveClass[]
  payments      Payment[]
  announcements Announcement[]

  @@map("batches")
}

model BatchSubject {
  id        String @id @default(uuid())
  batchId   String
  subjectId String

  // Relations
  batch   Batch   @relation(fields: [batchId], references: [id], onDelete: Cascade)
  subject Subject @relation(fields: [subjectId], references: [id], onDelete: Cascade)

  @@unique([batchId, subjectId])
  @@map("batch_subjects")
}

enum EnrollmentStatus {
  ACTIVE
  EXPIRED
  CANCELLED
}

model Enrollment {
  id         String           @id @default(uuid())
  userId     String
  batchId    String
  status     EnrollmentStatus @default(ACTIVE)
  paymentId  String?
  enrolledAt DateTime         @default(now())
  expiresAt  DateTime?

  // Relations
  user  User  @relation(fields: [userId], references: [id], onDelete: Cascade)
  batch Batch @relation(fields: [batchId], references: [id], onDelete: Cascade)

  @@unique([userId, batchId])
  @@index([userId])
  @@index([batchId])
  @@map("enrollments")
}

// ── Payments ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

enum PaymentStatus {
  PENDING
  SUCCESS
  FAILED
  REFUNDED
}

model Payment {
  id                  String        @id @default(uuid())
  userId              String
  batchId             String
  amount              Float
  currency            String        @default("INR")
  razorpayOrderId     String        @unique
  razorpayPaymentId   String?
  razorpaySignature   String?
  status              PaymentStatus @default(PENDING)
  receipt             String?
  createdAt           DateTime      @default(now())
  updatedAt           DateTime      @updatedAt

  // Relations
  user  User  @relation(fields: [userId], references: [id], onDelete: Cascade)
  batch Batch @relation(fields: [batchId], references: [id], onDelete: Cascade)

  @@index([userId])
  @@index([razorpayOrderId])
  @@map("payments")
}

// ── Live Classes ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

model LiveClass {
  id                String   @id @default(uuid())
  title             String
  description       String?
  batchId           String
  scheduledAt       DateTime
  duration          Int      // minutes
  meetLink          String?
  agoraChannelName  String?
  recordingLessonId String?  @unique
  isActive          Boolean  @default(true)
  createdAt         DateTime @default(now())
  updatedAt         DateTime @updatedAt

  // Relations
  batch           Batch   @relation(fields: [batchId], references: [id], onDelete: Cascade)
  recordingLesson Lesson? @relation("LiveClassRecording", fields: [recordingLessonId], references: [id], onDelete: SetNull)

  @@index([batchId])
  @@index([scheduledAt])
  @@map("live_classes")
}

// ── Notifications ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

enum NotificationType {
  CLASS_REMINDER
  TEST_RESULT
  NEW_CONTENT
  PAYMENT_CONFIRMED
  DOUBT_REPLY
  ANNOUNCEMENT
}

model Notification {
  id        String           @id @default(uuid())
  userId    String
  title     String
  body      String
  type      NotificationType
  isRead    Boolean          @default(false)
  data      Json?
  createdAt DateTime         @default(now())

  // Relations
  user User @relation(fields: [userId], references: [id], onDelete: Cascade)

  @@index([userId, isRead])
  @@index([createdAt])
  @@map("notifications")
}

model NotificationPreference {
  id             String  @id @default(uuid())
  userId         String  @unique
  classReminder  Boolean @default(true)
  testResult     Boolean @default(true)
  newContent     Boolean @default(true)
  paymentConfirm Boolean @default(true)
  doubtReply     Boolean @default(true)
  announcement   Boolean @default(true)

  // Relations
  user User @relation(fields: [userId], references: [id], onDelete: Cascade)

  @@map("notification_preferences")
}

// ── Doubts ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

enum DoubtStatus {
  OPEN
  ANSWERED
  CLOSED
}

model Doubt {
  id         String      @id @default(uuid())
  userId     String
  lessonId   String?
  questionId String?
  text       String      @db.Text
  imageUrl   String?
  status     DoubtStatus @default(OPEN)
  createdAt  DateTime    @default(now())
  updatedAt  DateTime    @updatedAt

  // Relations
  user    User         @relation(fields: [userId], references: [id], onDelete: Cascade)
  lesson  Lesson?      @relation(fields: [lessonId], references: [id], onDelete: SetNull)
  replies DoubtReply[]

  @@index([userId])
  @@index([status])
  @@map("doubts")
}

model DoubtReply {
  id        String   @id @default(uuid())
  doubtId   String
  userId    String
  text      String   @db.Text
  imageUrl  String?
  createdAt DateTime @default(now())

  // Relations
  doubt Doubt @relation(fields: [doubtId], references: [id], onDelete: Cascade)
  user  User  @relation(fields: [userId], references: [id], onDelete: Cascade)

  @@index([doubtId])
  @@map("doubt_replies")
}

// ── Announcements ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

model Announcement {
  id        String   @id @default(uuid())
  title     String
  body      String   @db.Text
  batchId   String?
  createdBy String
  createdAt DateTime @default(now())

  // Relations
  batch   Batch? @relation(fields: [batchId], references: [id], onDelete: SetNull)
  creator User   @relation("AnnouncementCreator", fields: [createdBy], references: [id], onDelete: Cascade)

  @@index([batchId])
  @@map("announcements")
}

// ── D-Chemistry Specific ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────

model FlashCard {
  id       String @id @default(uuid())
  topicId  String
  front    String @db.Text
  back     String @db.Text
  category String
  imageUrl String?
  order    Int    @default(0)

  // Relations
  topic Topic @relation(fields: [topicId], references: [id], onDelete: Cascade)

  @@index([topicId])
  @@map("flash_cards")
}

model FormulaSheet {
  id          String  @id @default(uuid())
  chapterId   String
  title       String
  pdfUrl      String?
  htmlContent String? @db.Text
  order       Int     @default(0)

  // Relations
  chapter Chapter @relation(fields: [chapterId], references: [id], onDelete: Cascade)

  @@index([chapterId])
  @@map("formula_sheets")
}

// ── AI Chatbot ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

model ChatConversation {
  id        String   @id @default(uuid())
  userId    String
  title     String
  context   String   @default("academic") // academic, general, doubt
  createdAt DateTime @default(now())
  updatedAt DateTime @updatedAt

  // Relations
  user     User          @relation(fields: [userId], references: [id], onDelete: Cascade)
  messages ChatMessage[]

  @@index([userId])
  @@map("chat_conversations")
}

model ChatMessage {
  id             String   @id @default(uuid())
  conversationId String
  role           String   // user, assistant
  content        String   @db.Text
  createdAt      DateTime @default(now())

  // Relations
  conversation ChatConversation @relation(fields: [conversationId], references: [id], onDelete: Cascade)

  @@index([conversationId])
  @@map("chat_messages")
}
